\\\(y_{n+2} − 1.6\,y_{n+1} + 0.6\,y_n = h \,(5\,f_{n+1} − 4.6\,f_n) \\\)

to approximate {@'y(tn2)@}.

\\\({@'y(tn2)@}\approx\\\) [[input:S_yn2]] [[validation:S_yn2]] [[feedback:yn2]]]]></text>
